        "col6_Is this target a net zero target?": "No, but it is a mid-term target towards our net zero target",
        "col7_Are carbon credits currently used or planned to be used to achieve this target?^": "No, this target will not use carbon credits",
        "col11_Year target was established": 2023.0,
        "col12_Emissions covered by target in year target was established (metric tonnes CO2e)": 16832507.0,
