        "col21_Specify if target is considered a science-based target (SBT) and the SBT methodology it aligns to": "No, our jurisdiction does not consider the target to be science-based (select future intention to set a SBT): Other: ICLEI South Asia's ClimateResilientCITIES Methodology",
