        "col3_Name of plan and URL link, if applicable^": "Bhavnagar Climate Resilient City Action Plan\\n\\nhttps://drive.google.com/file/d/1g_Si7P6RwFpzyuNfF60ZMEjDmK2aR5AW/view?usp=drive_link",
        "col4_Confirm attachment/link provided to plan": "The plan has been attached and can be accessed (unrestricted) on the link provided",
