        "col3_Describe how the factor supports or challenges the adaptive capacity of your jurisdiction": "Mumbai faces in addressing climate change and sustainability is the lack of access to high-quality, relevant data from various stakeholders operating across the city. This challenge stems from limited climate literacy and awareness among certain sectors, which can hinder effective data collection, sharing, and integration into citywide climate initiatives. Reliable data is essential for making informed decisions, tracking progress, and designing targeted interventions."
