        "question_text": "Has a climate risk and vulnerability assessment been undertaken for your jurisdiction? If not, please indicate why.^",
        "Has a climate risk and vulnerability assessment been undertaken for your jurisdiction? If not, please indicate why.^": "Yes, a climate risk and vulnerability assessment has been undertaken"
