        "col3_Describe how the factor supports or challenges the adaptive capacity of your jurisdiction": "The city does not have a dedicated climate or resilience budget line, and climate-related projects must compete with core service-delivery investments. Limited own-source revenues and dependence on state and national schemes constrain the ability to co-finance or scale adaptation projects and to prepare bankable proposals for external climate finance. Currently city has established city climate action cell, which will recommend climate projects and aim to integrate into budget (ongoing)"
