        "col1_Indicate the energy-related assessments that have been undertaken for your jurisdiction^": "Other: A Sustainable Energy Action Plan (SEAP) for Coimbatore City Municipal Corporation's electricity consumption from various municipal facilities is prepared, which addresses affordable and sustainable energy. Please refer attached document named Sustain",
        "col2_Total energy consumption (MWh)": 7444209.64,
        "col3_Total energy consumption from renewable energy sources (MWh)^": 1000.0,
