        "col3_Describe how the factor supports or challenges the adaptive capacity of your jurisdiction": "Multiple risks requires multiple set of solutions to address them. While prioritising the actions, it is always a mere challenge for GHMC to allot budgets as the operational costs of the existing infrastructure are soaring high and mobilising resources with a limited budget is a constraint, which delays the execution of the actions and associated results. Delay in execution will further increase the estimated costs which in turn adds weight to budget. "
