        "col6_Description of metric / indicator used to track goal and evidence of implementation": "1. Treated wastewater can be utilized in horticulture for\\nirrigation purposes and landscaping across the city\\n2. Industries within GIDC 1 & 2 can use treated wastewater\\nfor non-potable purposes like washing equipment,\\nvehicles, and facilities, reducing demand on freshwater\\nsources.\\n3. Implementing a dual piped system in group housing to\\nensure the reuse of treated wastewater for non-potable\\nuses like gardening and flushing\\n4. Junagadh Agriculture University (JAU) can utilizes\\ntreated wastewater for irrigation in agricultural research\\nfields and demonstration plots",
