        "col3_Describe how the factor supports or challenges the adaptive capacity of your jurisdiction": "Tirunelveli City Municipal Corporation has low revenue collection efficiency and the revenue fund is not enough to meet the annual expenditure by the city for all basic urban services. The city is dependent on the state government to meet its funding gaps and this could be a challenge to the adaptive capacity of the city against climate change. "
