        "col4_Describe the impacts on vulnerable populations and sectors": "The combination of urbanization, tourism growth, and climate change impacts increasing the water stress day by day. In each summer the city administration have to make arrangements of water tankers in some particular parts of the city and the population that can afford water tankers they have to manage it by their own due to the less water supply. The water stress can increase health impact and Hygiene and Sanitation issues in vulnerable groups, it can also increase issues related to Time and Energy Burden (women and girls), Economic and Livelihood, Social Conflicts etc.",
