        "col15_Is this target publicly available?": "Other: Vijayawada Net-zero Climate Resilient City Action Plan is attached. The target for this sector is compared with the business-as-usual scenario by 2047. Link - https://drive.google.com/file/d/1SC8ITuhFl41CndU8e2TYueebcxKJNxPY/view",
        "col16_Progress made towards target": "In the present baseline year, Vijayawada withdraws 250 MLD of water from the Krishna River, with a maximum withdrawal capacity of 263 MLD. The city aims to reduce its freshwater demand from 243 MLD (projected for 2030) to 205 MLD by 2030. This reduction will be achieved by supplementing the additional water demand through rainwater harvesting, reusing treated wastewater, and regulating groundwater extraction.\\n\\nThe Vijayawada Net-zero Climate Resilient City Action Plan Annexure report provides 'Key Performance Indicators' against each action to monitor and evaluate the achievement of proposed targets (See Annexure L, pages 84 to 109). "
